page.title: 06SURVEY OF FOOD
page.content: SURVEY OF FOOD:A TWELVE YEAR OLD Jane Smith of 1L surveyed what she had to eat for 1 week. This is what she had for Breakfast,Lunch,and Evening meal. {BREAKFAST LUNCH EVENING MEAL {_________ _____ ____________ Cornflakes 2 Salad Meat pie 2 sandwich 3 Toast 4 Pizza 1 Potatoes 6 Porridge 1 Hot_dog 1 Peas 3 Egg and Meat pie 1 Sprouts 2 bacon 1 Carrots 2 Bacon Stew 1 sandwich 1 Sausages 1 Oranges 2 Liver 1 Cakes and biscuits 4 Hamburger 1 The number refers to the number of times Jane Smith ate particular foods.
